            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[750ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1L]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641915122682-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
