            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Once the peas have warmed through, add most of the<strong> chopped parsley</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and mix everything together – this is your <strong>chorizo, pea & sun-dried tomato orzotto</strong></p>",
