            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chorizo, pea & sun-dried tomato orzotto</strong> with the <strong>balsamic salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>remaining parsley</strong>, season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
